   <summary>This extension helps magento merchants have Sezzle as a payment option</summary>
   <description>Users will be able to checkout using Sezzle to &quot;buy now and pay later&quot;.

Visit https://www.sezzle.com to know more about Sezzle.</description>
   <license>MIT</license>
   <license_uri/>
   <version>2.0.4</version>
   <stability>stable</stability>
   <notes>In this version here are the highlights:
1. Change payment type to quote based instead of order based. So user&apos;s cart doesn&apos;t get empty when coming back from Sezzle pay if they wish to not pay using Sezzle.
2. Any failed sezzle payment is out of payment list.
3. Refunds can be made online.
4. Support for onestepcheckout.</notes>
